name: Steampunk alien wool coat
description:
This coat is made of wool fabric with leather decoration on front. It has belt. Has two side pockets with snap-magnet closure. Closure for the coat is snap-magnets, very easy to open and close. It is made with viscose fabric lining. The design has a bit puffy sleeves and the cut of coat is A type, but with accented waistline.
Originally in grey, but can be ordered in different colours.

Made to order, allow 5 weeks for production.
Upon purchase the following measurements have to be provided: shoulder to shoulder, bust, waist, hips, length, sleeve width, sleeve length

name: Pale pink leather bullet corset
description:
This corset is made of real pale pink leather, decorated with two bone channels in black on front and back. It has fake bullets decoration on front (3 places, two bullets). This corset is made of three layers or material (leather, inside cotton layer, lining). Closure on back with lacing. It has sturdy pink corset rope for lacing. For 58cm corset there are 15 bones, 6 spiral steel, 9 spring steel. For larger sizes there is more boning.
This corset can be worn for tight lacing and waist training. It reduces waist for 8 cm maximum.

Made to order, allow 3 weeks for production.
Upon purchase the following measurements have to be provided: underbust, natural waist, hips, corset side length.

name: Steampunk cabaret ruffles skirt
description:
This skirt is made of black corduroy fabric. It has 3 layers of ruffles, decorated with black lace. It's shorter on front and longer on back. It can be fully opened with snap buttons, which are also closure for this skirt.
It can be worn on low-waist and also as high waist skirt. 

Made to order, allow 3 weeks for production.
Upon purchase the following measurements have to be provided: waist, hips, length on side.

name: Black clockwork cameo steel boned waist cincher
description:
This waist cincher - corset is made from sturdy black cotton fabric, detailed with real leather, spaghetti wires and clock mechanism parts. On front is cameo made from real leather, spaghetti wires and clock parts. On back is lacing with D-rings. This cincher has lining.
This waist cincher is not made for waist training, but since it has STEEL boning (8 pieces, 4 on side), it may give support and cinch your waist depending on your measures. (for real corsets it's suggested to order ~10cm, 2-4inch smaller corset size than your natural waist size)

Made to order, allow 3 weeks for production.
Upon purchase the following measurements have to be provided: underbust, waist, hips, cincher side length.

name: Steampunk military victorianesque jacket
description:
Jacket is made of black corduroy fabric. From waist the cut goes down as a half-circle. Shoulders and back are decorated with epaulette type detailing in black and gold fringe and rope. The cut is fitted and flattering. Unlined (Can be lined for extra fee). Closure with two buttons on front.

Made to order, allow 3 weeks for production.
Upon purchase the following measurements have to be provided: shoulder to shoulder, bust, waist, hips, length, sleeve width, sleeve length
